                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>\n                                                  <sic>Pittsburg</sic>\n                                        </placeName>\n                                        <date>December 14<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1852</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Rev I. Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">by our last meeting of our<lb/> Congregation it\n                                        has been resolved to advertise in<lb/> your Occident for a\n                                        shochet teacher &amp; chasan<lb/> you will please then and\n                                                  <add>?</add> the following adverti<lb/>sement in\n                                        your Occident for three times and send<lb/> me by letter\n                                        your charge for the same <sic>wich</sic> you shall<lb/>\n                                        receive by return mail</p>\n                              <p>Wanted by the German Jewish Congregation Sharay\n                                                  Shomajim<add>?</add><lb/> of\n                                                  <placeName><sic>Pittsburg</sic> Pa.</placeName> a\n                                        Competent person to officiate as<lb/> chasan shochet &amp;\n                                        teacher salary 250 Dollars per annum<lb/> he must bring\n                                        satisfactory testimonial and the term<lb/> to\n                                                  <sic>comence</sic> on first of <date>April</date>\n                                        next for <sic>farther</sic><lb/> information <sic>aply</sic>\n                                        by letter Post paid.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName role=\"author\">N. Gallinger</persName>\n                                        here<lb/> our most <add>?</add> is to get a Good teacher for our<lb/>\n                                        <sic>youts</sic> as they are till now <sic>verry</sic>\n                                        ignorant of our<lb/>\n                                        <sic>relition</sic></p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I am sir Respectfully yours</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(5)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">N. Gallinger</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>N. D. Abr. <persName>Leeser</persName> I want to <sic>inquir</sic>\n                                        of you in the same time<lb/> about <persName>Mr E.\n                                                  Marcusson</persName> that Gentleman is here\n                                        chasan<lb/> &amp; shochet by Polish Kahl and it has been\n                                        hindet to<lb/> our Rahl that the Polish Kahl <sic>wand</sic>\n                                        to unite</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3jd4q878/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
