                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>with our Rahl, <sic>wich</sic> I believe would be a Good thing<lb/>\n                                        for better and I <sic>understoot</sic> that they want our\n                                        Kohl to<lb/> engage <persName>Mr Marcuson</persName> as\n                                        their chasan, it has nothing more<lb/> been said about it\n                                        and I for my part are not<lb/>\n                                        <sic>aquainted</sic> with <persName>Abr\n                                                  <add>?</add></persName> no more than\n                                        <add>?</add><lb/> I did so in your <sic>Occitend</sic> but\n                                        understood that he<lb/> could not teach the children the\n                                                  <sic>pronosation</sic> of<lb/> the German\n                                                  <del>teacher</del> reading <sic>wich</sic> would\n                                        be an objective<lb/> Now sir I wish you would be so kind\n                                        when you<lb/> let me know the amount of the advertisement\n                                        to<lb/> give <sic>privatly</sic> your <sic>oppinion</sic> as\n                                        I think you are<lb/> well <sic>aquainted</sic> with\n                                                  <persName>Mr Marcuson</persName></p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(5)\">I remain yours</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(6)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">N Galinger</persName>\n                              </p>\n                    </body>\n          </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3jd4q878/canvas/p2"
